	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002078_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right">1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> Oct<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> 1864 </p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>NEWSTEAD ABBEY,</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>MANSFIELD</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">NOTTS. </p>
<lb/><p>Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Tidman</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I called yesterday 
<lb/>at <placeName>Blomfield St.</placeName> &amp; 
<lb/>unfortunately missed 
<lb/>meeting you. I thank 
<lb/>you for your kind 
<lb/>note. I did not 
<lb/>answer it because 
<lb/>I was in <placeName>Scotland</placeName> &amp; 
<lb/>as I was to be only 
<lb/>one day in <placeName>London</placeName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I thought it best 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002078_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>to save trouble by 
<lb/>waiting on you. </p>
<lb/><p>If you <choice><sic>recieve</sic><corr>receive</corr></choice> any 
<lb/>information from 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Moffat</persName> or about 
<lb/>him I shall feel 
<lb/>much obliged by 
<lb/>your communicating 
<lb/>it at your convenience 
<lb/>as I have heard nothing 
<lb/>from him or from 
<lb/><persName>John Moffat</persName> for 
<lb/>a long time. Wishing 
<lb/>you better health &amp; every blessing<reg>.</reg></p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002078_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>Rev<hi rend="sup underline">d</hi> D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Tidman</persName></p>
			
</div>
